Package it.polimi.se2.clupapplication.services

Class StoreService

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.se2.clupapplication.services.StoreService
@Service
public class StoreService
extends java.lang.Object
This class acts as an intermediate between the controllers and the Store entity. It's called from the controllers, it passes the request to the entities and return back the fetched objects.

    • deleteSlot

      public boolean deleteSlot​(Store store, java.lang.Long slotId) throws java.lang.IllegalAccessException
      Delete a certain slot of a specified store.
      Parameters:
      store - the store whose slot has to be deleted.
      slotId - the slot id to be deleted.
      Returns:
      true if the process is successful, false otherwise.
      Throws:
      java.lang.IllegalAccessException - if the request comes from a manager that is not the owner of the specified store.
